'''铝汞齐'''（Aluminium amalgam）是[[铝|铝]]在金属[[汞|汞]]中的[[溶液|溶液]]。

==性质==
中性。与水激烈反应，放出[[氢气|氢气]]。

==制取==
无油铝丝（片）用稀[[氢氧化钠|氢氧化钠]]洗净到强烈放出氢气时，用水粗洗一次，然后用0.5％[[氯化汞|氯化汞]]溶液处理一至两分钟。重复上述过程一次，即得汞齐化的光亮金属丝（片）。依次用水、[[乙醇|乙醇]]、[[乙醚|乙醚]]快速冲洗后，即可立即使用。现用现制。<ref>{{cite journal en | journal = [[Clays_and_Clay_Minerals|Clays and Clay Minerals]] | year = 1971 | volume = 19 | pages = 337–339 | title = Use of aluminum-amalgam in mineral synthesis at low temperatures and 1 atmosphere total pressure | author = Ward Chesworth | url = http://www.clays.org/journal/archive/volume%2019/19-5-337.pdf | doi = 10.1346/CCMN.1971.0190510 | access-date = 2009-10-02 | archive-date = 2011-05-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110516091302/http://www.clays.org/journal/archive/volume%2019/19-5-337.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref> {{cite journal en| doi = 10.1016/j.tetlet.2005.03.106 | title = A new, practical and efficient sulfone-mediated synthesis of trifluoromethyl ketones from alkyl and alkenyl bromides | author = Lourdes Muñoz, Esmeralda Rosa, Ma Pilar Bosch and Angel Guerrero | journal = [[Tetrahedron_Letters|Tetrahedron Letters]] | volume = 46 | issue = 19 | year = 2005 | pages = 3311–3313}} </ref>

也可用需要还原的底物与铝箔、氯化汞、無水乙醇和干燥的无硫苯溶剂[[回流|回流]]，直接完成底物的还原反应。

==用途==
用作[[还原剂|还原剂]]，特别适用于对碱敏感的羰基化合物的还原，如酮酸酯、烷基芳基酮还原成相应的醇酸酯和嚬哪醇；脱除不饱和碳上的磺酰基等。<ref>{{cite book|pages=8–9|title=有机合成试剂制备手册|location=成都|publisher=四川工业出版社|isbn=7-5614-0066-7|author=黄枢等编著|date=1988年8月}}</ref>

